Tutorial on using ATLAS Toolkit
1. Go to Github, copy the whole repo
2. git clone it on desired location "git clone https://github.com/atlas-nano/ATLAS-toolkit.git"
3. enjoy

Tutorial on using the scripts
0. prepare your files by using zip "zip -r dmp_cube /home/ye/sims/my_project/ag_slab/DMP-cube"
1. scp the desired file from the file folder to expanse home directory "scp np.zip imazalov@login.expanse.sdsc.edu:/home/imazalov"
2. unzip the file "unzip ..."
3. Use the script "perl /home/imazalov/ATLAS-toolkit/scripts/combineBGFs.pl -b "1.bgf 2.bgf 3.bgf 4.bgf 5.bgf 6.bgf 7.bgf 8.bgf 0.bgf" -s comb_dmp_ag.bgf"
4. scp it back to the desktop "scp imazalov@login.expanse.sdsc.edu:/home/imazalov/np/comb.bgf ."
5. done

