How to create lammps input files
1. create a bash alias on the supercomputer
2. have a ff directory with certain files
3. createLammpsInput -b comb_dmp_slab.bgf -f "/home/imazalov/rimse24/ffs/dmp-v2.gaff.ff /home/imazalov/rimse24/ffs/AgEAM.ff" -s dmp_slab_run
4. 
